if I was making you unpopular?

16:33.741 --> 16:36.691
You lied to me.
- Careful Meghan!

16:36.741 --> 16:39.691
That's slander, as you should
know from your TV show...

16:39.741 --> 16:40.891
Suits!

16:40.941 --> 16:44.211
It's because you still have
feelings for him, don't you?

16:44.261 --> 16:45.491
Don't be ridiculous.

16:45.541 --> 16:48.331
Yes, you do! And you're
trying to break us up.

16:48.381 --> 16:50.051
Well, you'll never do it.

16:50.101 --> 16:52.621
And I'm going to that Hollyoaks audition.

16:53.741 --> 16:55.611
Break a leg!

16:55.661 --> 16:58.331
What was that all about?
- Time of the month? - Oh, right.

16:58.381 --> 17:00.811
She'll be fine at the
audition, by the way. - Oh, yes?

17:00.861 --> 17:04.131
Yeah. Offered the producer a knighthood.

17:04.181 --> 17:06.701
Fancy some pie?
- Yes...

17:08.101 --> 17:10.300
.. I do.

17:14.781 --> 17:16.771
Oh, there you are.

17:16.820 --> 17:18.651
How was last night?

17:18.701 --> 17:22.330
Oh, I bumped into some old uni friends.

17:22.381 --> 17:24.371
Where were you?

17:24.421 --> 17:27.131
The same.

17:27.181 --> 17:30.171
I'll stand, actually. It's
better for the old circulation.

17:30.221 --> 17:31.731
Right.

17:31.781 --> 17:34.531
'The Duchess of Cambridge has
controversially taken heroin

17:34.581 --> 17:36.901
and streamed it live across the world.

17:37.941 --> 17:40.731
But her shock tactics seem to have worked,

17:40.781 --> 17:43.611
and eradicated Scotland's
unique drug problem.

17:43.661 --> 17:45.851
Addicts are throwing away their needles,

17:45.901 --> 17:47.571
dealers are becoming postmen,

17:47.621 --> 17:48.981
and this, from Afghanistan

17:54.981 --> 17:57.781
I've solved the drug problem
that was unique to Scotland!

17:59.941 --> 18:03.811
